	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hi, I recently bought a Famicom version of Bandit Kings of Ancient China and sent it over to Leon from nesreproductions.com to have it made into a Rockman 4 : MI cart. It seems to work well, however there is a graphical glitch I've found that occurs every time I encounter a boss on Cossack 2 or 3(I forget which one). This graphical glitch does not occur in nestopia or FCEUX.<br /><br />Is this related to inaccurate MMC5 emulation? Or maybe the cart was miswired somehow? I found this a bit unlikely because everything else seems to work.<br /><br />here's a clip of the bug in action :<br /><a href="http://www.hitbox.tv/video/403419" class="postlink">http://www.hitbox.tv/video/403419</a>

		

		</td>
