	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Thats 'normal'.  Mine has it, and there are a couple of other small graphical glitches but nothing game breaking.  Its common that extensive hacks have a few graphic screw ups here because if it works on an emulator, its not 100% guaranteed to be perfect on the console.  Some are major, some are minor.  This one is minor.

		

